Gtk2::Ex::DateSpinner is a simple date entry widget using spin buttons
for year, month and day.  The prerequisites are Gtk2-Perl and
Date::Calc.  The DateSpinner home page is

    http://www.geocities.com/user42_kevin/gtk2-ex-datespinner/index.html

Bug reports to the author at user42@zip.com.au please.
